Package applications

Class Application

  • java.lang.Object
    • applications.Application
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Mnist, XorGate
    public abstract class Application
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class describes an Application or a usecase for a NeuralNetwork, and its subclasses acts as a way to train a NeuralNetwork in a there specified Application or usecase using the AppliedNetwork class.
    Author:
    OdinhengeT
    See Also:
    AppliedNetwork, NeuralNetwork, Mnist, XorGate
